{"prompt": "Develop a site for a community theatre group. The visuals should be expressive and include a marigold yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Community Players Theatre</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #fef6e0; /* Light background */\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .header {\n            background-color: #ffb300; /* Marigold yellow */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #ff8f00; /* Darker marigold */\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #ffb300;\n            padding-bottom: 5px;\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n        .upcoming-shows, .about-us, .contact {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .show-card {\n            background-color: #fff8e1; /* Lighter marigold */\n            border: 1px solid #ffb300;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n        .show-card img {\n            max-width: 120px;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n        }\n        .show-info h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #f57f17; /* Even darker marigold */\n        }\n        .show-info p {\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #ff8f00; /* Darker marigold */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #e65100; /* Even darker marigold for hover */\n        }\n        .contact-info p {\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n        }\n        .footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            background-color: #ffb300; /* Marigold yellow */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .header h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .show-card {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                text-align: center;\n            }\n            .show-card img {\n                max-width: 100%;\n                margin-bottom: 15px;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header class=\"header\">\n        <h1>Community Players Theatre</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"about-us\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>Welcome to the Community Players Theatre, where passion for performance comes alive! We are a dedicated group of local artists, volunteers, and theatre enthusiasts committed to bringing engaging and diverse theatrical experiences to our vibrant community. From classic dramas to contemporary comedies, we strive to entertain, inspire, and spark conversation through the magic of live theatre.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"upcoming-shows\">\n            <h2>Upcoming Shows</h2>\n            <div class=\"show-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/120x160/FFD700/FFFFFF?text=Play1\" alt=\"Poster for Play 1\">\n                <div class=\"show-info\">\n                    <h3>\"A Midsummer Night's Dream\"</h3>\n                    <p><strong>Dates:</strong> July 15 - July 30, 2024</p>\n                    <p><strong>Venue:</strong> The Grand Auditorium</p>\n                    <p>Experience Shakespeare's most beloved comedy, filled with fairies, lovers, and hilarious mistaken identities.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Buy Tickets</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"show-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/120x160/FFD700/FFFFFF?text=Play2\" alt=\"Poster for Play 2\">\n                <div class=\"show-info\">\n                    <h3>\"The Lighthouse Keeper's Daughter\"</h3>\n                    <p><strong>Dates:</strong> September 10 - September 25, 2024</p>\n                    <p><strong>Venue:</strong> The Studio Theatre</p>\n                    <p>A poignant new drama exploring themes of isolation, connection, and the enduring power of hope.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Buy Tickets</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-info\">\n                <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Theatre Lane, Our Town, CA 90210</p>\n                <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (555) 123-4567</p>\n                <p><strong>Email:</strong> info@communityplayerstheatre.org</p>\n                <p>Follow us on social media for the latest updates!</p>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Visit Our Facebook</a>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer class=\"footer\">\n        <p>&copy; 2024 Community Players Theatre. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic interactive elements could be added here if needed\n        // For example, a simple fade-in effect for sections\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n            const sections = document.querySelectorAll('.container section');\n            sections.forEach((section, index) => {\n                section.style.opacity = '0';\n                section.style.transform = 'translateY(20px)';\n                setTimeout(() => {\n                    section.style.transition = 'opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out';\n                    section.style.opacity = '1';\n                    section.style.transform = 'translateY(0)';\n                }, index * 100); // Stagger the fade-in\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>"}